ong></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><p style="white-space: normal;margin-bottom: 5px;margin-top: 5px;line-height: 1.5em;text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(2, 30, 170);font-size: 17px;"><strong style="line-height: 1.6;font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="color: rgb(2, 30, 170);font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>1 中国70年生育政策演变：从鼓励到严控到放松再到构建生育支持体系</strong></span></strong></span><o:p></o:p></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin-bottom: 5px;margin-top: 5px;line-height: 1.5em;text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(2, 30, 170);font-size: 17px;"><strong style="line-height: 1.6;font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="color: rgb(2, 30, 170);font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>2 生育情况：生育率低迷，年轻人生育意愿低，育龄妇女规模下滑，出生人口连续下滑</strong></span></strong></span><o:p></o:p></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin-bottom: 5px;margin-top: 5px;line-height: 1.5em;text-indent: 2em;"><span style="text-align: justify;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0.48px;font-family: 微软雅黑;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-size: 17px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 17px;text-align: justify;font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(0, 0, 255);letter-spacing: 0.48px;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-weight: 400;overflow-wrap: break-word;">2.1 生育率：年轻人生育意愿低，一孩生育率持续下降、二孩政策消退、三孩政策效果未显现</span></strong></span><o:p></o:p></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin-bottom: 5px;margin-top: 5px;line-height: 1.5em;text-indent: 2em;"><span style="text-align: justify;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0.48px;font-family: 微软雅黑;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-size: 17px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 17px;text-align: justify;font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(0, 0, 255);letter-spacing: 0.48px;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-weight: 400;overflow-wrap: break-word;">2.2 育龄妇女：婴儿潮人口逐渐退出育龄阶段，90后渐成生育主力</span></strong></span><o