: normal;font-weight: 400;overflow-wrap: break-word;">4.4 日本：传统性别分工激化工作与家庭矛盾，总和生育率跌破1.3，陷入“低生育陷阱”</span></strong></span><o:p></o:p></p><p style="margin-right: 0pt;margin-left: 0pt;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 10.5pt;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(2, 30, 170);font-size: 17px;"><strong style="line-height: 1.6;font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="color: rgb(2, 30, 170);font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>5 启示：全面放开并鼓励生育刻不容缓，加快构建生育支持体系，切实减轻生养育孩子负担</strong></span></strong></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin-bottom: 5px;margin-top: 5px;line-height: 1.5em;text-indent: 2em;"><span style="text-align: justify;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0.48px;font-family: 微软雅黑;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-size: 17px;"><strong><span style="text-align: justify;font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(0, 0, 255);letter-spacing: 0.48px;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-weight: 400;overflow-wrap: break-word;"></span></strong></span></p><div style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 0px;"><div powered-by="xiumi.us" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><div style="text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;width: 530.475px;box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;overflow: hidden !important;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 303.3 4.6" style="vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;" width="100%"><g style="box-sizing: border-box;"><g style="box-sizing: border-box;"><g style="box-sizing: border-box;"><g style="box-sizing: border-box;"><path style="box-sizing: border-box;" d="M189.5,1.8c-1.4,0-2.7,0-4.1-0.3c-0.6-0.1-1.2-0.2-1.7-0.5c-0.3-0.1-1.5-1.3-1.3-0.4      c-0.4-0.4-1.2-1.2-1-0.1c0.1,0.4,0.6,1,0.6,1.4c0,0.1,0,0.3,0,0.4c0,0.1,0,0.2,0,0.4c0,0.4-0.5,1-