ormal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-weight: 400;overflow-wrap: break-word;">2.5 人口结构变动带来住房价值的分化，人口或人才流入的核心城市住房价值凸显</span></strong></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;margin-bottom: 5px;margin-top: 5px;line-height: 1.5em;text-indent: 2em;"><span style="text-align: justify;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0.48px;font-family: 微软雅黑;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-size: 17px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 17px;text-align: justify;font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(0, 0, 255);letter-spacing: 0.48px;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-weight: 400;overflow-wrap: break-word;">2.6 住房改善时代来临，从“有房住”到“住好房”、产品力成为购房者关注的重点</span></strong></span></p><div style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 0px;"><div powered-by="xiumi.us" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><div style="text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;width: 530.475px;box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;overflow: hidden !important;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 303.3 4.6" style="vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;" width="100%"><g style="box-sizing: border-box;"><g style="box-sizing: border-box;"><g style="box-sizing: border-box;"><g style="box-sizing: border-box;"><path style="box-sizing: border-box;" d="M189.5,1.8c-1.4,0-2.7,0-4.1-0.3c-0.6-0.1-1.2-0.2-1.7-0.5c-0.3-0.1-1.5-1.3-1.3-0.4      c-0.4-0.4-1.2-1.2-1-0.1c0.1,0.4,0.6,1,0.6,1.4c0,0.1,0,0.3,0,0.4c0,0.1,0,0.2,0,0.4c0,0.4-0.5,1-0.6,1.3      c-0.2,1.1,0.6,0.3,1-0.2c-0.1,0.9,1.1-0.2,1.3-0.4c0.5-0.2,1.2-0.4,1.7-0.5c1.3-0.3,2.7-0.3,4.1-0.3c2.8,0,5.5-0.1,8.3-0.1      c1.8,0,97.5-0.1,99.1,0.4c0.6,0.2,1.7,0.8,2.4,0.5c0.9-0.4-0.5-0.9-0.8-1.3c0.2-0.4,1.7-0.9,0.8-1.3c-0.6-0.3-1.8,0.3-2.4,0.5      c-1.7,0.5-97.3,0.4-99.1,0.4C195,1.9,192.3,1.8,189.5,1.8z" fill="rgb(0,2,103)"></path></g><g styl